snippet.title: Getting Started with python basics
snippet.description:
Hello Guys,
This is the first video of Python-3 Tutorials. In this Video we will learn Basics of python like how to code open what is in it names of different components any much more you must know before programming.
As promised here is link to PDF of this section:
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1UnrIr2Suadl8nCTvtAmb8T2ufGW0zTs6/view?usp=drivesdk
Just go and read it .

Link of PDF of All Tutorials: 
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1UnrIr2Suadl8nCTvtAmb8T2ufGW0zTs6/view?usp=sharing

It will definitely help you a lot in upcoming sections.

Enjoy the Tutorials…

And don’t forget to subscribe to “Code Academy '' Youtube Channel and also hit the Like button.
Thank you guys.
